You can have a fabulous programmer,

00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:22.320
but if his attitude is of the fallen

00:07:22.320 --> 00:07:24.280
arms, more than the same, of

00:07:24.280 --> 00:07:26.520
not leaving comfort missions,

00:07:26.520 --> 00:07:27.880
because maybe he is not the person

00:07:27.880 --> 00:07:29.020
you want, because maybe he

